channel.title: Tibia
channel.description:
Hey Hey whats up my fellow Moparscapers!
So this is going to be a thread about Tibia!
Tibia is a very old free to play MMO that came out in 1997 and is still receiving updates and has an active player base to this day!
Here's a screenshot of what Tibia looks like, excuse the old-school graphics style xDD
[img]http://images.mmosite.com/feature/tibia/picture/big/1.jpg[/img]
Do any of you play Tibia, or have you ever played tibia? I would be very interested to find out! I personally made my account in 2006 and have been playing it on-and-off since! :D
